OL,3,CPC became 'number one victim' of hate
OL,4,Ccrime in force area
OL,6,FThe organisation representing rank and
OL,7,Ffile police officers says it is
OL,8,F"absolutely disgusting" that a
OL,9,Fconstable has been subjected to more
OL,10,Fthan 20 racist incidents in the last
OL,11,Fthree years.
OL,13,FPC Mourad Karaouani, a Humberside
OL,14,FPolice officer based at Bridlington,
OL,15,Fsays he was abused so frequently that
OL,16,Fhe was offered a move to another
OL,17,Fstation.
OL,19,FAt one point he was statistically the
OL,20,Fnumber one victim of hate incidents in
OL,21,Fthe force area.
