OL,3,CPC became 'number one victim' of hate
OL,4,Ccrime in force area
OL,6,FHumberside Police Federation chair Lee
OL,7,FSims described PC Karaouani's
OL,8,Fexperience as "absolutely disgusting".
OL,10,F"No police officer should ever be
OL,11,Fsubject to racist abuse while they are
OL,12,Fcarrying out their duty to protect the
OL,13,Fpublic," he said.
OL,15,F"One incident is one too many, there
OL,16,Fis no room for this in society and our
OL,17,Fcolleagues do not come to work to
OL,18,Fsuffer any hate crime. There is simply
OL,19,Fno excuse for this abuse, and it must
OL,20,Fstop."
