OL,6,FPC Karaouani joined the force after
OL,7,Fworking as a firefighter for five
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FHe said he had experienced suspects
OL,11,Fsaying they did not want him to
OL,12,F"touch" them because of his skin
OL,13,Fcolour.
OL,15,FHe said: "As a new officer, I was
OL,16,Fthinking, is it something I do that
OL,17,Fmakes people hate me? Is it the way I
OL,18,Fspeak to people? I'd go back to my
OL,19,Fstation, put my body-worn video on and
OL,20,Fwatch the way I interacted with
OL,21,Fpeople. It made me doubt myself.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
