OL,6,F"It was happening so often that it was
OL,7,Freviewed by supervisors, and it was
OL,8,Festablished that there was definitely
OL,9,Fnothing that I was saying that was
OL,10,Finstigating that kind of hate, it was
OL,11,Fjust because of my skin colour."
OL,13,FIn one incident in May 2024, PC
OL,14,FKaraouani was on night shift when he
OL,15,Fwas attacked by a woman as he tried to
OL,16,Fbreak up a fight between two men
OL,17,Foutside a nightclub.
OL,19,FHe said: "She was shouting and
OL,20,Fscreaming in my face, calling me all
OL,21,Fthe words you can imagine."
