OL,6,FBodycam footage showed the woman
OL,7,Ftelling fellow officers she would not
OL,8,Fattack them because they were white.
OL,10,FPC Karaouani, who spoke out after a
OL,11,Fsurvey by the police federation found
OL,12,Fmore than half of ethnic minority
OL,13,Fofficers had been racially abused on
OL,14,Fduty, turned down an offer to transfer
OL,15,Fto Hull following the incidents.
