OL,6,FHe said: "I like my team here, and if
OL,7,FI go somewhere else just because it's
OL,8,Feasier for me, what about other
OL,9,Fofficers? What about other people that
OL,10,Fcome to Bridlington to live, and who
OL,11,Fare from different minorities or have
OL,12,Fa different skin colour?
OL,14,F"Why do I have to move somewhere else
OL,15,Fto avoid those kinds of incidents? In
OL,16,Ffact, those people need to change
OL,17,Ftheir mindset."
