OL,6,FHe added: "People need to know that
OL,7,Fthese kinds of incidents are real,
OL,8,Fthey do happen, and there are some
OL,9,Fpeople who still have that kind of
OL,10,Fmentality.
OL,12,F"Just because you lost your temper or
OL,13,Fyou had an issue, it doesn't give you
OL,14,Fthe right to start insulting people
OL,15,Fand giving them abuse."
OL,17,FChief Constable Chris Todd said there
OL,18,Fwas "no room" for racism and
OL,19,Fencouraged staff to report abuse.
